    <item>
      <title>中国问题恶化之际阿斯利康大力宣扬美国增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/astrazeneca-talks-up-us-growth-as-china-problems-worsen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯利康公司曾经快速扩张的中国业务因一项调查而放缓，该公司股价也因此受到重创，因此该公司越来越希望从美国寻求增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/astrazeneca-talks-up-us-growth-as-china-problems-worsen</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:53:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汤姆·斯泰尔谈论特朗普和美国清洁能源的未来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-12/tom-steyer-on-trump-and-the-future-of-us-clean-energy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Galvanize Climate Solutions 联合创始人 Tom Steyer 讨论了当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对能源生产和投资的潜在影响、美国清洁能源的商业和经济效益以及人工智能对全球电力消费的影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-12/tom-steyer-on-trump-and-the-future-of-us-clean-energy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:34:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍勃·戴蒙德预计特朗普政府将减少银行监管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-12/bob-diamond-expects-less-bank-regulation-under-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Atlas Merchant Capital 首席执行官 Bob Diamond 预计，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普在银行监管方面不会那么激进，并表示地区性银行需要整合，因为大多数公司“规模太小，无法取得成功”。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-12/bob-diamond-expects-less-bank-regulation-under-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:30:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Elliott 持有霍尼韦尔 50 多亿美元股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/elliott-amasses-5-billion-plus-stake-in-honeywell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 已在霍尼韦尔国际公司 (Honeywell International Inc.) 持有超过 50 亿美元的股份，并正在推动这家工业巨头进行分拆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/elliott-amasses-5-billion-plus-stake-in-honeywell</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:20:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰森食品预计 2025 年鸡肉销量将超过牛肉销量，业绩将更加强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/chicken-turnaround-prompts-tyson-to-forecast-better-year-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰森食品公司 (Tyson Foods Inc.) 第四季度盈利超出预期，且预计明年业绩将更加强劲，其鸡肉业务的好转抵消了牛肉业务的损失，股价随之飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/chicken-turnaround-prompts-tyson-to-forecast-better-year-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 12:31:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔选择卡塔尔投资局美洲区负责人管理 5100 亿美元基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/qatar-names-mohammed-al-suwaidi-head-of-500-billion-wealth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔任命穆罕默德·阿尔索瓦迪 (Mohammed Al Sowaidi) 为其 5100 亿美元主权财富基金的首席执行官，该基金将在未来几年获得更强大的金融实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/qatar-names-mohammed-al-suwaidi-head-of-500-billion-wealth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:27:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行将加强对银行地缘政治风险的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/ecb-is-set-to-step-up-focus-on-geopolitical-risks-at-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行监管负责人克劳迪娅·布赫 (Claudia Buch) 已开始对该机构施加影响，欧洲央行计划要求银行提供更多有关其地缘政治风险敞口的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/ecb-is-set-to-step-up-focus-on-geopolitical-risks-at-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:05:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>与对冲基金有关联的公司收购日产汽车 2.5% 股份后，日产汽车股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/nissan-surges-after-cayman-affiliated-firm-takes-2-5-interest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一位激进投资者购入这家陷入困境的日本汽车制造商 2.5% 的股份后，日产汽车公司的股价创下 15 年来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/nissan-surges-after-cayman-affiliated-firm-takes-2-5-interest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 06:10:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧和美元走强导致油价维持在近一个月低点附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国需求前景疲软、美元走强以及市场担心市场可能转向供应过剩，油价在前两天大幅下跌之后，目前维持在本月低点附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 23:28:27 GMT</pubDate>
